     - Phase 46: real DB-backed plugin marketplace
     - Phase 47: real team workspace
     - Phase 48: P0–P2 completion / production hardening pack
   - Update Current Runtime Summary:
     - /marketplace is real DB-backed with dry-run action runner
     - /team is real team workspace
     - plugin execution remains dry-run/sandbox-gated
     - strategy promotion remains disabled by default unless explicitly enabled
   - Update CHANGELOG.md with Phase 48 entry.
   - Update docs/releases/FINAL_RELEASE_NOTES.md and docs/releases/PHASE42_FINAL_PUBLIC_RELEASE.md or create docs/releases/PHASE48_P0_P2_COMPLETION.md.
   - Update docs/reports/PHASE_TRACEABILITY_MATRIX.md if present.

2. Phase 47 report correction
   - Update docs/reports/PHASE47_REAL_TEAM_WORKSPACE_REPORT.md.
   - Remove stale “Backend service tests: N/A” and “Backend API tests: N/A”.
   - Replace with actual current status:
     - backend service/API tests present and passing
