     - rollback notes
     - remaining explicitly deferred items, if any

Implementation requirements:
- Keep changes minimal and deterministic.
- Prefer shell/Python stdlib for release scripts.
- Scripts must be executable.
- Generated artifacts must not contain secrets.
- All new docs must be markdown.
- Do not remove existing safety language.
- Do not weaken safety gates.
- Do not introduce paid external services.

Backend technical requirements:
- backend/app/backtesting/models.py:
  - OptimizationRequest.parameter_grid must be Field(default_factory=dict)
- backend/app/backtesting/optimizer.py:
  - SORT_METRICS must include max_drawdown_percent
  - Sorting must use ascending order for max_drawdown_percent and descending for reward metrics
- backend tests:
  - no duplicate test names
  - no missing fixtures
  - all tests must pass under python -B -m pytest -q

Frontend technical requirements:
- frontend/src/api/endpoints.ts:
  - runOptimization must normalize parameter_grid to {} if missing, null, array, or non-object
  - preserve existing API envelope client semantics
- frontend build must pass:
  - npx tsc -p tsconfig.build.json --pretty false
  - npm test
  - npm run build

Makefile targets to add or update:
- sbom
- backup-restore-proof
- release-attestation
- p0-p2-completion-check
- phase48-validate

phase48-validate must run at least:
- backend ruff format --check
- backend ruff check
- backend pytest
- frontend tsc/build/test if dependencies are installed
- safety scan / forbidden tracked files check if existing target exists
- verify-p0-p2-completion.sh

Validation commands:
- cd backend && python -m ruff format --check app tests
- cd backend && python -m ruff check app tests
- cd backend && mypy app --ignore-missing-imports
- cd backend && python -B -m pytest -q
- cd frontend && npx tsc -p tsconfig.build.json --pretty false
- cd frontend && npm test
- cd frontend && npm run build
- make phase48-validate
- make validate-fast

Acceptance criteria:
- P0 optimize issue fixed: /api/backtesting/optimize no longer fails validation when parameter_grid is omitted.
- No duplicate tests.
- No missing pytest fixtures.
- README includes Phase 46, Phase 47, Phase 48.
- Phase 47 report is corrected and no longer says backend tests are not created.
- P2 docs/scripts exist for SBOM, SLOs, incident response, backup/restore proof, dependency policy, release attestation.
- Makefile exposes phase48-validate.
- All modified shell scripts are executable.
- No secrets printed.
- No .env files tracked.
- make validate-fast passes.
- CI expected green.
